OL,3,CNext government urged to scrap Legacy
OL,4,CAct as legal challenge begins
OL,6,FThe next Westminster government has
OL,7,Fbeen urged to scrap the Legacy Act and
OL,8,Flisten to the victims of the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Troubles.
