OL,6,FEarlier this year, a High Court judge
OL,7,Fruled that one of the central elements
OL,8,Fof the Act, the provision for
OL,9,Fconditional immunity from prosecution
OL,10,Ffor Troubles offences, should be
OL,11,Fstruck out.
OL,13,FThe Northern Ireland Troubles (Legacy
OL,14,Fand Reconciliation) Act passed into
OL,15,Flaw in September.
OL,17,FFrom May 1, all civil cases and
OL,18,Finquests that were not at their
OL,19,Ffindings stage were halted.
