OL,6,FResponsibility for investigating all
OL,7,Flegacy cases has since been
OL,8,Ftransferred to a new truth recovery
OL,9,Fbody, the Independent Commission for
OL,10,FReconciliation and Information
OL,11,FRecovery (ICRIR).
